race.comment: Tough competitive race to end the day. BUNDEENA (4) excellent fresh gelding who ticks plenty of boxes today. Fitted with the one 742m trial placing at Randwick and look for him finishing over the top of them. POWER OF THE BRAVE (6) away only fairly and failed to gain any real momentum around Moonee Valley when seventh over 955m. Fitter now and look for him taking control early from the good draw. Big weight drop with Stanley's claim and can give a ton of cheek. DUROVA (8) sharp Scone-trained mare who keeps raising the bar on the country and provincial circuit. Returns from a let-up and since fitted with a searching 900m trial placing on the heavy track at Scone. SOUTH OF INDIA (1) smart sprinter resuming. Has the speed to get across from the wide draw and will give plenty of cheek in the going. Each way.
